# Alex bundle sync (mandatory)

**Any change to `alex-*.mdc`** must end with:

1. `./scripts/sync-alex-personality.sh`
2. Commit **`.cursor/personas/alex-personality.md`** in the same change as the rules.

CI runs `./scripts/check-alex-personality.sh` on every PR. **Production** (employee-factory) reads the bundle from the **`geeemoney/cursor-rules`** image.

**Optional:** uncomment the line in **`.cursorignore`** for `alex-personality.md` locally to avoid duplicate context while editing—still commit the tracked file.

Full policy: **`cursor-rules-maintenance.mdc`** (Alex Slack bundle).
